35
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,239
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti Marine.

36
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,400
[SPEAKER_00] Oke, nisam ovako zamišljao.

37
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:53,840
